haha, so I'll update you guys on my life since march 26th...

I went to Prom. Jeff was quite the amazing date... haha. After that my life basically consisted of Jeff and Tyler every day. LOSed it up a few times. Need to do that again so if my lovely LOS people see this pick a date.

Summer thank god... I've seen Jeff and Tyler every day all but three days each... Then I went to six flags with Aly it was such a good time.

Then the LOVELY jamie spinello is now at my house for  10 days, she came on tuesday of last week.. shes awesomee and shes making me update this.. idk why though. tuesday we went out to eat at my marys... then came home hung out with tyler jeff and lauren at some playground. wednesday we went out to eat and then went to gregs and then i had a bunch of people go over my house to suprise her. didn't turn out as well as i planned but it was very fun. Then Thursday night me jeff tyler and lauren went to old mystic village, then lickety splits and back to my house to watch team america... then the next day we went to newport all day it was just me lauren and jamie. Then later that day Tyler came to my house and we went to jamestown to see fireworks but then never ended up doign that cause they were postponed so we went back to newport and walked around and ate at panara bread.... then  saturday I suprised Jamie by having her sister Lauren come and we went to the zoo, beach, out to eat and mini golfing. much fun. and then Jeffrey came over that night and we all talked and had a really good time we went to stop and shop and got food and pigged out.. then yesterday... bad day.... Jeff and Tyler came over but decided that it'd be really cool to be mad at me for no reason and then when I tried to talk to them and figure out what I did they didn't feel like telling me but whatever so lauren kicked them out ... then we went out to eat.. and came home and went to Will's party. Which was so much fun. It started out boring but then once we all started hanging out it was fun. Talked with Katy a lot. met some new people. idk it was a really good time. they're a fun group of people

now its fourth of July !! We're gonna get ready and go out for most of the day I think, then going to the fireworks laterr! Hoping to see a lotttttt of people!


Happy 4th!

Three day weekend. I love it.

Except for the fact i have like 100 projects due this week that I haven't started any of them yet.

Thursday night we picked up Aly and Me her and Lauren went bowling with TJ Gary Dave Jeff Mark and Tyler. Had an INTEREsTING ride home. i'll leave it at that.

Friday hung out with Aly.

No clue whats happening today call the cell if you wanna haang out 7412496

jane

Today was boring. IPS was okay. Aly and my spaghetti tower barely even holds the box. Oh well. we suck. 

World civ =  horrible. I hate those fishbowl things.

Housing we played jokes on stee--veeen. It was fun. I dont mind that class ever.

lunch was nice with just the trio. yeahh..

Spanish is so dumb! Mrs. Risley gets so mad at me for talking and then i stop and just mind my own business and shes like LIVEN UP JANE! shes gay. ihaterher.

After school Me Lauren Matt and Greg went to Applebees and ate a bunch of food. It was fun. Matt and greg fight so much. GOD GREG GET YOUR FEET OFF MY SIDE haha... oh well. I love when its just us and the boys, too bad Josh isn't apart of the "crew" anymore. he was always so much fun.

Saturday I went out to eat with Kelly and my parents at some wiiicked fance place, they had a harp player. I loved it. I was kinda not feeling great though but it was still fun.

Sunday me and Lauren picked up my cousin and went to the championship game. dissapointing loss but thats okay. Then we went out to eat at the pizza place. I love Jordan and Lauren. It's always a good time when we're together. During dinner Kelly called, shes been so depressed over the loss of dan so she needed to get out of the house. so when we left I went food shopping with her and then we went to blockbuster got shall we dance, it wasnt too bad. Then I watched that all night and fell asleep. i'm really tired today though. Oh wellll.

I WANT SUMMER.
SNOW SUCKS.

With Lauren and Dan both having their license, its great. But I mean. Dan's obviously apart of the family. Just to think that with him driving around something bad could happen to him or lauren. Thats really scary. I care about them both way too much, and love them both. It's so scary to know that when Dan leaves my house he's not leaving in the company of my dad or when lauren leaves his house my dads not there in the drivers seat to pick her up. I guess it's stupid but I just get nervous sometimes watching them drive. Especially when I see Dan struggling to get out of my driveway. The poor kid tries to use the turn around since my driveway is HORRIBLE to get out of everyone knows it, but the snow is so bad that he just gets stuck there and has to attempt to get himself out. and It probably doesn't help feeling like you're being watched and not knowing what to do. Then I have to watch him finally get himself out, then back out instead of being turned around and then get stuck at the top because he didnt press the gas as hard as he could to get out of the driveway cause you have to do that too. Then he FINALLY gets out after he realized he needed to press on the gas. It all basically made me wanna cry. My mom made him promise he'd call when he got in. I really hope he does. Just to know he's okay. I mean, it's really nerveracking with lauren cause shes my older sister and all but I know how she drives cause I had to spend six months with her driving everyone around everywhere and I've been out in the car with her. So maybe thats why I sound like I'm more worried about Dan when he's driving. It's just scary. I've always been like that though. When it's snowing or raining really hard and its thundering and lightening and my parents arent home I'll sit on the couch in front of the window and every 30 seconds I'll turn around to see if the car comes down the driveway. And everytime I see an ambulance on the road I think of everyone thats not with me, like if I was on my way to the mall with Kelly and I saw one and Lauren or one or both of my parents were out I'd immediately think of them, and it always makes me wanna call them. It doesnt help that everytime you turn the news on theres always bad news about car accidents or on the radio with all the traffic interuptions. I feel really lame thinking like that but it's the way I am.

Anyways the phone just rang and it was Dan. So he's home.

The week back to school was lame. I hate school. I want summer. I've been so tired lately I don't even want to do anything. Even if it's hanging out with friends. I don't know whats wrong with me. 

Twenty-four days until my birthday! 

I'm gonna go now that I feel alot better.

Last night I went to the games, It was fun, but I was in a pretty bad mood so it wasn't as fun as it could of been. Afterwards I just went home. I was real upset from everything and then the car ride home just killed me. I got home and wouldn't talk to anyone, I went upstairs for awhile and thought I was okay so I just went and watched tv, and I just started balling my eyes out. My mom came in trying to get what happened out of me but I couldn't talk to her about it cause I know she would just get really mad, if not at me then at Kelly, and the other thing that was wrong wasn't really anything important. She kept asking me questions like, did someone hurt you or was someone mean to you, did you have a bad time tonight whats wrong. I wanted to be like why don't you ask your daughter she should know, but I just kept shaking my head no. Then she told me If i needed to talk to promise that she'd talk to her and thent old me she was a good listener. Then she left and I watched a movie. Was way too tired to finish it and I went upstairs to sleep. Lauren got back from Dans and came in my room and woke me up and she was like.. Are you okay, and I told her to go away and that i was too tired, and she was like I just wanna make sure you're okay and that nothing bad happened and you're not in trouble. so I promised her I wasn't in trouble and she kissed me on the cheek and left. I love that they care but, sometimes I know that  if i say something about it it won't make me feel better, just talking about things doesn't always work , especially in this case. I feel okay this morning Mainly because Kelly isn't home. The whole time I was downstairs she kept saying stuff about it and my parents just kept getting mad so that was another reason I wasn't gonna open up to them. And she kept trying to figure out what was wrong. I just wanted to turn around and tell her it was all her fault but I would of regretted it. I know by talking to Lauren she would just tell me the same thing kelly did, in a less harsh, and not screaming kind of way. Lauren's always so much nicer and understanding, but I know it's the truth, it's just .. hard.

Well, anyways, I'm done complaining... 

Whoever is commenting anonymously, you're part of the reason I was upset last night, just stop cause it's not even funny anymore. you're not cute, i tried to be nice about everything but you're just really immature and you comeplain about me and my friends being stuck up and snobby and saying we're always mean to people but then you turn around and are completely the same way towards us for no reason. So please just stop.

- jane
